	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65022455"><p>Exceptions Prove the Rules.</p><p>The law isn't there for the rules, it is to flesh out the exceptions. The rules seem clear and absolute, until they don't.</p><p>Simple rule: Do not kill</p><p>Exception: it's okay if you're defending your own life</p><p>Exception to the exception: unless you started the fight</p><p>And this goes on and on until it is complex string of exceptions to the otherwise simple rule.</p></div>
	</div>

