	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65022433"><p>I used to have to file taxes in the US. The IRS tax instructions also need to be precise, yet they somehow manage to make them understandable to ordinary people. Which makes sense, since ordinary people have to follow the instructions.
